name: Intellectual Asset Group
overview: IAG is the premier intellectual property (IP) transactions and Development Company. IAG establishes close, long-term relationships with global technology companies, research institutions, and private equity firms to capitalize and/or enhance their respective patents and technology. With a global team of patent attorneys, scientists, engineers and technologists, IAG takes the lead in identifying, creating, and implementing client-specific license, sale, and acquisition programs as well as stand-alone spinout ventures. Its founders have more than 30 years of global IP transactions experience. IAG serves clients in more than 20 countries throughout the Americas, Europe and Asia
